description: |
    The :ref:`/plugins/prepare/artifact` plugin now automatically verifies
    that packages listed in test ``require`` or ``recommend`` (and explicit
    :ref:`/plugins/prepare/install` phases) were installed from the artifact
    repository. The check runs as an auto-injected
    :ref:`/plugins/prepare/verify-installation` phase after all artifact
    phases complete. Set ``verify: false`` on the artifact phase to opt out.
